original_title: Dan Cummins: Crazy with a Capital F
overview: No stranger to the stand-up stage or late-night talk shows, Dan Cummins has built his rep on being crazy when it comes to his comedy, and this off-the-wall set filmed live inside the Bing Crosby Theater in Spokane, Wash., doesn't disappoint.
title: Dan Cummins: Crazy with a Capital F
